snippet.title: Micro Machines: Mini Challenge Mayhem - Official Alpha Gameplay Trailer | Upload VR Showcase 2023
snippet.description:
The fun of Micro Machines is making its way to virtual reality! TRAC - Mini Challenge Mayhem will let you create your own Micro Machines tracks in VR, let you perform wicked stunts, and even features mixed reality tracks as well! Micro Machines Mini Challenge Mayhem is coming soon.

#GameTrailers #VR #SummerofGaming
